# Marker directives for appsettings.json.
#
# JSON files cannot host comments, so this unit emits sentinel-key
# pairs `"//scaffold-block-X-start": ""` immediately after the top-level
# opening brace. ASP.NET Core's IConfiguration loader tolerates unknown
# keys.
ANCHOR ^\{[[:space:]]*$
BLOCK serilog-config
BLOCK csp-defaults
